lyTime":"2021-02-10T07:11:52.000Z","msg":"佢唔係癈而被換走，而係太親中而被換走"},{"pid":"f71a962dc1f578d54586b2fe79f25fd01d8062c6","tid":2402004,"uid":193642,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f8950d1f3972e8db20602d032f52d9b271a2febf","tid":2402004,"uid":42283,"like":3,"dislike":3,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-10T06:55:34.000Z","msg":"處困境要務實 港獨不可行 衛奕信：香港勿成北京眼中威脅<br />\n<br />\n【明報專訊】任內曾處理六四事件後香港信心危機的前港督衛奕信，在倫敦寓所接受本報專訪時表示，香港當前面對的社會撕裂、政府管治困難、中港關係緊張等問題，嚴峻程度遠不及1989年六四後的問題；香港人應保持樂觀務實，眼前困境並非無法解決。他強調，港獨訴求「完全不可行」，無論香港在殖民地時期或是現在，成功的要訣就是政治上不要被北京視為威脅。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/pns/%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E/article/20170609/s00002/1496944481274/%E8%99%95%E5%9B%B0%E5%A2%83%E8%A6%81%E5%8B%99%E5%AF%A6-%E6%B8%AF%E7%8D%A8%E4%B8%8D%E5%8F%AF%E8%A1%8C-%E8%A1%9B%E5%A5%95%E4%BF%A1-%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E5%8B%BF%E6%88%90%E5%8C%97%E4%BA%AC%E7%9C%BC%E4%B8%AD%E5%A8%81%E8%84%85\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2F%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2581%259E%2Farticle%2F20170609%2Fs00002%2F1496944481274%2F%25E8%2599%2595%25E5%259B%25B0%25E5%25A2%2583%25E8%25A6%2581%25E5%258B%2599%25E5%25AF%25A6-%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E7%258D%25A8%25E4%25B8%258D%25E5%258F%25AF%25E8%25A1%258C-%25E8%25A1%259B%25E5%25A5%2595%25E4%25BF%25A1-%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E5%258B%25BF%25E6%2588%2590%25E5%258C%2597%25E4%25BA%25AC%25E7%259C%25BC%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%25A8%2581%25E8%2584%2585&d=9j7BdtwWq97OJFdF2FXGhXWT%2F8u5gjw5w0zJU6lVJ48%3D&h=a7272b6d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2F%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2581%259E%2Farticle%2F20170609%2Fs00002%2F1496944481274%2F%25E8%2599%2595%25E5%259B%25B0%25E5%25A2%2583%25E8%25A6%2581%25E5%258B%2599%25E5%25AF%25A6-%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E7%258D%25A8%25E4%25B8%258D%25E5%258F%25AF%25E8%25A1%258C-%25E8%25A1%259B%25E5%25A5%2595%25E4%25BF%25A1-%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E5%258B%25BF%25E6%2588%2590%25E5%258C%2597%25E4%25BA%25AC%25E7%259C%25BC%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%25A8%2581%25E8%2584%2585&h=